function Get-TrelloApiBaseUri {
<#
.SYNOPSIS
    Return base (root) URI to Trello API
.DESCRIPTION
    Author   : Dmitry Gancho
    Last edit: 11/10/2015
.EXAMPLE
    Get-TrelloApiBaseUri
