.DESCRIPTION
    Author   : Dmitry Gancho
    Last edit: 11/10/2015
.PARAMETER CardId
    Required.
    Card Name.
.PARAMETER Description
    Required.
    Card Description.
.PARAMETER Comment
    Optional.
    Card Comment.
.PARAMETER WebSession
    Optional.
    Authenticated Trello WebSession
